1. wirless adapter: NRF24L01
2. servo for control flow of the water: SG-90 (Controlled by PWM)
3. servo balance:  SG-5010 or MG-995 
4. microcontroller: STM-32("Getting started with STM-32 Hardware developer"
5. bldc for making water to flow:(to be controlled by PWM) https://botland.com.pl/silniki-bldc-bezszczotkowe/5188-silnik-bezszczotkowy-z-przekladnia-25dx43l-45-1-ze-sterownikiem-pwm-enkoder-5904422306052.html?cd=18298825651&ad=&kd=&gclid=CjwKCAjw-rOaBhA9EiwAUkLV4geQaOKKD-l3gYV5RXAct9NCja5nMiYdrZ1AbeNjEGxQzgFgSdMZxhoCbZYQAvD_BwE
6. accelerometer (checking the speed and swing): ADXL345 - (WE should make the schematic)
7. Connectors(for RC transmissions)
8. Power supply: 5 lit ion battery in series. And 3 this in parallel 
- 18V to BLDC 6V to Servo - 3.3V to STM
